track_notes: This is the easiest path to Pic de Aiglo F/AM-416. On wintertime you must use snowshoes. The summit is wide enought to set dipole antenna and the landscape is wonderfull
track_title: From West to East on the way to F/AM-432

track_notes: In winter when the regular path is too icy and you cannot walk because too dangerous, you must use this path.
A fine summit for little walk
